== Boss Rush ==

After defeating Deathtoll, a hidden Boss Rush mode becomes available:

'''Access:'''
1. Clear the game
2. New Game+ option appears
3. Select "Boss Rush" from Master's Shrine

'''Rules:'''
* Fight all 8 bosses consecutively
* No items between fights
* HP/Magic restored to 50% between bosses
* Best time saved

